annotations.description:
A channel made by a pair of laymen, with the sole purpose of sharing music and videos about the One Holy Catholic Church and her History, her fights and her endurance. The Militant Church, the Traditional Church, the Everlasting Church.

This channel fully subscribes to the Nicene Creed and acknowledges the supremacy of Peter's Chair, which is now occupied by Francis, the Roman Pontiff, over Christendom, as Christ willed it. We do NOT subscribe to sedevacantism or similar heresies, and as such they will not be tolerated.
